SUMMARY:Ecosocialism Working Group
DESCRIPTION:Join us biweekly for continued conversations about our strategies for ecosocialist politics and future projects. Ecosocialism promotes democratic control over all institutions that impact life and the environment.  Questions? Please contact greennewdeal@seattledsa.org . \nCheck back for RSVP and zoom links.
