SUMMARY:Hiking Club to Mount Si 🌹
DESCRIPTION:We’re socialists who hike! \nMay we’ll be hiking Mount Si (8.0 miles) in the North Bend area. Let’s enjoy some early season hiking. DSA membership not required. \nMeet in the Hilltop Red Apple parking lot. Snacks and transportation to the trail provided. \nRecommended pack list:\n* Hiking boots\n* Water\n* Lunch or snacks\n* Jacket\n* Map (Apple or Google offline download\, AllTrails)\n* Sunglasses (weather depending)\n* Rain coat (weather depending)\n* Phone battery pack (optional)\nSee REI day hiking checklist for additional recommendations
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/hiking-club-to-mount-si-%f0%9f%8c%b9/
