LAST-MODIFIED:20260402T200843Z
UID:10018345-1778342400-1778349600@seattledsa.org
SUMMARY:May Labor Social
DESCRIPTION:RSVP HERE \nParticipants in our two workshops today are invited to continue their discussion and share what they learned at this social just down the street at Outer Planet Brewing. Anyone is welcome whether you’re not a union member (yet)\, a long time union activist\, or anywhere in between. \nWe’ll also have members of our Unionize for Trans Rights campaign at the social to discuss their work! \nYou can register for the Build A Better Union panel (for current union members) or the New Organizer Training (for future union members)\, both immediately before this social!
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/may-labor-social/
LOCATION:Outer Planet Brewing\, 1812 12th Avenue\, Seattle\, 98122\, United States
CATEGORIES:Labor,New Member Friendly,Socials
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://seattledsa.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/admin-ajax.png
ORGANIZER;CN="SDSA Labor Working Group":MAILTO:labor@seattledsa.org
END:VEVENT
